{
  "stem": "27335.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we need people who could be trusted and who would go through physical and mental test for this kind of-- this kind of assignment and this kind of training and-- and operation.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then finally-- finally, when Tim Buck then supplied first Paul Phillips, who was also-- also Jewish, immigrated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think he came in '27, '28 in Canada.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- he was the head of the-- of the ethnic department of the party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took a national tour, you see, and he picked the proper people, you see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were very-- you know, the first were the Yugoslav groups-- 22 of them, the Croatian service and the Slovenians and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were trained and then out at Camp X.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That Camp X, it's between Whitby and-- and-- and Oshawa, that secret training camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And second group were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [? one ?] in nine was landed in-- in one group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they never trained two separate groups together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was always-- it was always a rule and a policy that the least people you know is the better.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that they just trained one-- one-- one group at-- at a time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we were approached-- when we were approached, it was 1922-- 1942-- with this agent what I told you about.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then it was all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We sensed that-- that our destination is Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] the question, he never told us--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not-- not that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was all our education, our knowledge of the language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot like you, you were asking me about my-- my knowledge about-- about the country and my-- my level of education and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How well I know the history of the country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after these-- these questions, well, we sensed it very real.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
